Entries.default: "And where has Vatnir run off to? He could not have gone far."
"Hey, where's that horny guy? At least we know we can't lose him in a crowd."
"The priest went and left his chapel? He can't hardly have gone far."
"Where'd the lad ship off to? Seemed too sickly to get far."
"Oor slabberin' lad's richt skiltered off. Dae ye spy 'im, Watcher?"
"Where did that goat-headed boy scamper off to? Maybe we can track him by the smell?"
"What a time for our talkative friend to disappear! Captain, he can't have gone far."
